Detailed Description

This is a sub-structure in CSL_Aif2PdCommonSetup. This structure is used for configuring the routing parameters of protocol decoder.

Uint8 CSL_Aif2PdRoute::RouteTs

OBSAI time stamp in header. Used to extend addressing by using the TS field The number of bits of TS to compare is controlled via the ctrl field.
